descriptionHtml:
Since I had to wipe my hard drive and make another, I\'ve decided to upload this here.
Requires Dawnguard. For Blood Potions though probably works without it too.
This is the chest I use for testing mods to make sure they function correctly.
It\'s Located In QAsmoke, you can reach this cell by opening the console and typing : coc QAsmoke
or you can place the chest at you by typing: help \"Crafting Supply Chest\" 4 in the console then type Player.placeatme xxxxxxxx 1 <-- x\'s being the ID. Anyways enjoy.
author: Watcherzero
